                            <b>About HN History</b>
                            <br>
                            <span>
                                I created HN History, because I too often remember
                                seeing something interesting on HN x days ago (where x is known)
                                and wanted to share it with someone, but was unable to find it again, because HN is fluid. <br>
                                <br>
                                All information gathered comes from HN's RSS feed.
                                It's a little limiting. It does not provide the points of the post, or the OP.
                                For now the RSS will do, if this is of use to anyone other than myself, I might expand to parse the actual website.<br>
                                You can find its source <a href="https://github.com/scastaneda/hnhistory">on GitHub</a>.<br>
                            </span>
                            <br>
                            <span><b>What's with the 'Actual Date' ?</b></span><br>
                            
                            <span>
                                If a date beyond HN History is selected,
                                it returns the lastest HN History grabbed.<br>
                                <br>
                                If a date before HN History was created(April 13th, 2014) is selected,
                                it returns the first of the HN History.<br>
